## User Story

As a **user**, I want to see a placeholder image when an item doesn't have an image, so that the UI remains clean and user-friendly.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: If an item has no image, a default "No Image Available" image should be shown.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: The placeholder image should be styled similarly to other images.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Add a default image to the project assets.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Update the front-end to show the placeholder image if no image is available for an item.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: Low
- **Related Issues**: #107
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Consider adding an option for users to upload their own images for items.
